org.activebpel.rt.wsdl.def
Interface IAePropertyAlias

All Known Implementing Classes:
AePropertyAliasImpl
public interface IAePropertyAlias

This interface represents a Message Property Alias extention element. It contains information about operations associated with this Property Alias element.
